  "comment": "BBP59 Battery Uplight Par 9x 12W IP65: The BBP59 is a compact Battery Par ideal for use as accent and uplighting. The BBP59 is IP65 rated and hence for outdoor and indoor use. It’s equipped with 9x super bright 12W RGBAW-UV LEDs and comes fitted with a removable built-in battery which will last up to 18 hours when fully charged, depending on colours and intensity. The adjustable foot can be fixed in different angles for angular placement of the par. The BBP59 can communicate in a variety of ways, with IR and wireless DMX. This makes the units easy to connect to each other.",
